Package model

package model
  • Class
    Description
    Administrator
    The Administrator class represents an administrator user in the system.
    Appointment
    The Appointment class represents a scheduled appointment between a doctor and a patient.
    AppointmentDetail
    The AppointmentDetail class extends the Appointment class, providing additional details about the doctor and patient involved in the appointment.
    AppointmentOutcome
    The AppointmentOutcome class represents the outcome of an appointment, including details such as the patient, appointment, type of service provided, and consultation notes.
    AppointmentOutcomeDetail
    The AppointmentOutcomeDetail class extends AppointmentOutcome, providing detailed information about an appointment outcome, including the associated appointment and any prescribed medications.
    BaseEntity
    The BaseEntity class provides a base structure for entities in the system.
    Doctor
    The Doctor class represents a doctor in the system, extending the User class with additional attributes for working hours.
    Entity
    The Entity interface defines the basic contract for entities in the system.
    MedicalRecord
    The MedicalRecord class represents a medical record in the system, containing details about the patient, doctor, record type, and specific information about the record.
    MedicalRecordDetail
    The MedicalRecordDetail class extends MedicalRecord, providing additional details about the doctor associated with the medical record.
    Medicine
    The Medicine class represents a medication in the system, with attributes for name, stock level, and a low stock alert threshold.
    Nurse
    The Nurse class represents a nurse in the system, extending the User class.
    Patient
    The Patient class represents a patient in the system, extending the User class.
    PatientVital
    The PatientVital class represents the vital signs of a patient, including measurements such as blood oxygen level, height, weight, and blood pressure.
    PendingPrescription
    The PendingPrescription class represents a prescription that is yet to be fulfilled.
    Pharmacist
    The Pharmacist class represents a pharmacist in the system, extending the User class.
    Prescription
    The Prescription class represents a prescription issued during a medical appointment, including details such as the associated appointment outcome, medicine, status, and amount.
    PrescriptionWithMedicine
    The PrescriptionWithMedicine class extends Prescription, providing additional details about the medicine associated with the prescription.
    ReplenishmentRequest
    The ReplenishmentRequest class represents a request to replenish the stock of a specific medicine.
    ReplenishmentRequestDetail
    The ReplenishmentRequestDetail class extends ReplenishmentRequest, providing additional details about the specific medicine and pharmacist involved in the request.
    User
    The User class serves as an abstract base class for user entities in the system.
